data.description: Move-in ready home on large lot with no back neighbors.  Hardwood flooring in tandem formals and family room. Family room with fireplace, built-ins and window wall to the back yard is open to the island kitchen and breakfast area with access to the large covered patio.  Master down, game room and 3 large bedrooms up. Pool sized back yard for all your outdoor pleasures. Walden is on Lake Houston with shopping, dining and entertainment in Atascocita. Humble Schools.
